Myreveil by damien laurent v1.0

Usage: make or make re

Alarm: --set new alarm: ./add [hour:min]
       --mange all alarms: nano input
       --see all alarms: cat input

start myreveil: ./myreveil
start myreveil background ./myreveil &

When the alarm is ringing a new file will be generated for ex: 10+10,
to stop it juste type ./set_result [result]
   	   	      ex: ./set_result [20]
and if the result is good the song will be stopped and, the file generated will be destroyed

